"All of the officers

415
00:37:34,731 --> 00:37:36,160
"were from outside
the local area,

416
00:37:36,170 --> 00:37:38,144
"and it probably had not
entered their minds

417
00:37:38,154 --> 00:37:40,768
"that almost all of us
were named McDonald.

418
00:37:40,778 --> 00:37:43,040
"Nobody moved except for
the shuffling of feet.

419
00:37:43,050 --> 00:37:45,319
The red roo"...Hey.

420
00:37:45,386 --> 00:37:47,616
- Hello, there.
- Kristy. We met on your tour.

421
00:37:47,626 --> 00:37:49,153
How's Mrs. Andersson?
Has she settled in?

422
00:37:49,163 --> 00:37:51,265
I'm wondering if I could have

423
00:37:51,275 --> 00:37:53,313
a moment of your time
to ask your advice?

424
00:37:53,323 --> 00:37:55,552
Oh, sure. I was just
reading to Mr. Burke here.

425
00:37:55,562 --> 00:37:56,832
Maybe when we finish this chapter,

